-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/bidens-israel-visit-reveals-inconvenient-truths-about-shift-in-u-s-israel-relationship/0000018b-41b7-d881-abab-edbf96650000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯的新中东梦想破灭</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/hamas-puts-paid-to-dreams-of-a-new-middle-east/0000018b-41b8-d242-abef-53bebaf90000</link><description>只要伊朗不介入冲突，世界经济就能应对以色列最近战争的影响</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 07:48:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/hamas-puts-paid-to-dreams-of-a-new-middle-east/0000018b-41b8-d242-abef-53bebaf90000</guid></item><item><title>拜登与内塔尼亚胡一起表示，以色列没有轰炸加沙医院</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article-live/israeli-army-blames-islamic-jihad-for-hitting-gaza-hospital-in-deadly-strike/0000018b-40a6-d881-abab-edae5c5d0000</link><description>美国总统拜登在加沙医院爆炸造成数百人死亡后抵达以色列 ■ 真主党宣布针对以色列的“前所未有的愤怒日” ■ 约旦取消与美国、埃及、巴勒斯坦领导人的峰会 ■ 哈马斯向以色列城市发射火箭弹，以色列国防军称进行了数十次空袭■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，至少有 1,300 名以色列人被杀 ■ 哈马斯：3,200 名巴勒斯坦人被杀，约 11,000 人受伤</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 04:12:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article-live/israeli-army-blames-islamic-jihad-for-hitting-gaza-hospital-in-deadly-strike/0000018b-40a6-d881-abab-edae5c5d0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登对以色列的拥抱使他走上了与阿拉伯世界发生冲突的道路</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/bidens-embrace-of-israel-sets-him-on-a-collision-course-with-the-arab-world/0000018b-3f5e-dcae-afaf-7ffef5730000</link><description>美国总统对以色列的全力支持以及他全权授权以色列在加沙地带开展行动，这使得他的政府与邻国阿拉伯国家发生冲突，这些国家担心战争可能蔓延到他们的领土</description><pubDate>Wed, 18 Oct 2023 03:00:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-18/ty-article/.premium/bidens-embrace-of-israel-sets-him-on-a-collision-course-with-the-arab-world/0000018b-3f5e-dcae-afaf-7ffef5730000</guid></item><item><title>作为战争努力的全面合作伙伴，美国寻求保护以色列免受